## Architecture in one screen

The two halves of every domain:

```
proto/services/<svc>/v1/<svc>.proto    ‚Üê API contract (annotated)
                ‚Üì forge generate
gen/services/<svc>/v1/...               ‚Üê generated stubs (never edit)

handlers/<svc>/                         ‚Üê THIN translation layer
  service.go      validate, extract auth, proto‚Üîinternal, call service, map errors
  validators.go   pure request validators
  errors.go       domain error ‚Üí connect.Code

internal/<svc>/                         ‚Üê BUSINESS LOGIC
  contract.go     Service interface + domain types
  service.go      implementation
  errors.go       domain-typed sentinels and error types
  *_gen.go        mocks/middleware/tracing/metrics from forge generate
```

